Package io.permazen.parse.expr

Class CastNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.permazen.parse.expr.CastNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Node
    public class CastNode
extends Object
implements Node
    A parsed cast expression.

    Includes an extension to support casting a String to any supported field type via FieldType.fromString(java.lang.String), for example (java.time.Duration)"PT24H".
